{"tid":207062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有錢買車無錢租車位個啲人係咩心態？","createTime":"2017-04-18T17:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T01:42:14.000Z","uid":45252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ade2089e0a203c316a7bc4a78bc33a903e11379","tid":207062,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:39:02.000Z","msg":"有錢買車，無錢養車<br />\n車位又租唔起，四圍泊，影響交通<br />\n即係叫個社會幫你埋單啦<br />\n無錢租車位都要買車呢啲人咩心態？<br />\n<br />\n預左泊車撚比負評同埋嘈架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b5796aed84ad83f5a5f5182f73d5cfd921c9de","tid":207062,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"有時唔係唔想泊入場"},{"pid":"fbfdf99bc498ecb524a9d93e92dac07aed83a20e","tid":207062,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時唔係唔想泊入場</blockquote><br />\n黎，我準備聽你藉口架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e48063c65e5dbb472d79c3d7feb4ae38886b075","tid":207062,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講停車場無位之類嘅爛鬼藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你會唔會去宜家，買件家私，返到屋企先諗佢放邊？<br />\n&ldquo;呀屌原來無位放，是但搵個路邊放先&rdquo;<br />\n係咁既話我覺得你自制能力好有問題喎"},{"pid":"d70702b62144cdfb77f2ee83b65975ac76bd7f5d","tid":207062,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:00:33.000Z","msg":"其實有時搵車位唔係咁易<br />\n當然我係反對違例街泊"},{"pid":"a3cafea85ef7c2c2640ab414904731353ca41d26","tid":207062,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2b5796aed84ad83f5a5f5182f73d5cfd921c9de","tid":207062,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T17:39:52.000Z","msg":"有時唔係唔想泊入場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"有幾唔想呀，講啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}